        public ImportMissionV1PackageSort​(android.content.Context context,

        Construct an importer that works on MissionPackage/DataPackage files. Users of this class should either use .zip or .dpk for the mission package extension.
        Parameters:
        context - the extension to be used
        validateExt - if the extension needs to be validated
        copyFile - if the file needs to be copied
        bStrict - strict if the mission package is required to have a manifest
